item.title: Syi.cc warez script
item.dc:creator: @vortex vortex
item.description:
@vortex wrote:

Reines wrote it. It was a simple database where selected users (those who wanted) were able to put links to their files they had uploaded on rapidshare, with title, description and picture (eg. album cover) of the release. Then the script would generate a forum post from the given info. If you know how to code php/mysql, it shouldn’t be hard to create yourself.

tl;dr: i don’t have it anymore :b

  • http://web.archive.org/web/20060410055848/http://dl.syi.cc/
